abstract: Smylie Kaufman wins Shriners Hospitals for Children Open golf tournament at TPC Summerlin in Las Vegas; other golf news noted.
lead_paragraph: Smylie Kaufman won the Shriners Hospitals for Children Open in his fifth PGA Tour start, shooting a 10-under-par 61 to finish at 16-under 268 at T.P.C. Summerlin in Las Vegas.

headline.main: Shooting a 61 for His First Win
